 border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid #dddddd; border-right: 1pt solid #dddddd; height: 25.7pt;" valign="top">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000;">Lab Engineer</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 6pt; width: 349px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid #dddddd; border-right: 1pt solid #dddddd; height: 25.7pt;" valign="top">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15pt; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000;">Department of Electrical Engineering, Isra University, Hyderabad, Pakistan</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', '', 'irshad.memon@israuniversity.edu.pk', '', 'EE-028', 'Electrical Engineering', '2026-06-10 05:36:30', '2026-06-10 05:36:30', NULL);
INSERT INTO `teachers` (`id`, `name`, `designation`, `photo`, `sort_order`, `qualifications`, `description`, `current_positions`, `education`, `experience`, `publications`, `awards`, `email`, `contact_number`, `code`, `department`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `category`) VALUES (43, 'Mr. Ahmed Murtaza', 'Lecturer', 'teachers/mr_ahmed_murtaza.jpg', 9, 'PhD*, MPhil, M.Ed, B.A.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'ahmed.murtaza@israuniversity.edu.pk', '', 'EE-043', 'Electrical Engineering', '2026-06-10 05:36:30', '2026-06-10 05:36:30', NULL);
INSERT INTO `teachers` (`id`, `name`, `designation`, `photo`, `sort_order`, `qualifications`, `description`, `current_positions`, `education`, `experience`, `publications`, `awards`, `email`, `contact_number`, `code`, `department`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `category`) VALUES (45, 'Engr. Dr.Mukhtiar Ali Unar', 'Chairperson', 'teachers/engr_drmukhtiar_ali_unar.jpg', 1, 'Ph.D, M.Sc, BE', '<p>Prof. Dr. Mukhtiar Ali Unar is currently serving as Professor and Head of the Department of Electrical Engineering. Before joining Isra University, he served at Mehran University of Engineering and Technology (MUET), Jamshoro, where he held various academic and administrative positions, including Meritorious Professor, Director of the Institute of Information and Communication Technologies and Dean of the Faculty of Electrical, Electronic, and Computer Engineering.</p>\r\n<p>Dr. Unar earned his B.E. in Electronic Engineering from MUET and later obtained his M.Sc. in Electrical and Electronic Engineering and Ph.D. in Control Systems Design from the University&nbsp;of Glasgow, United Kingdom. He also completed postdoctoral fellowships at the University of&nbsp;Glasgow and the University of Strathclyde. With more than three decades of experience in&nbsp;teaching, research, and administration, he has contributed to curriculum development,&nbsp;postgraduate supervision, and institutional development in the field of engineering education.</p>\r\n<p>His areas of interest include artificial intelligence, control systems, data science, digital signal&nbsp;processing, and engineering education. He has authored and co-authored several research papers&nbsp;in national and international journals and has supervised numerous postgraduate theses. Dr. Unar also served as Chief Editor of the Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and&nbsp;Technology from 2008 to 2024. He continues to contribute to accreditation and quality assurance&nbsp;processes through his involvement with the Pakistan Engineering Council (PEC), National&nbsp;Computing Education Accreditation Council (NCEAC), and the Higher Education Commission&nbsp;(HEC).</p>', '<p>Professor and Chairman</p>', '<ul>\r\n<li>PhD, University of Glasgow, 1999</li>\r\n<li>M.Sc., University of Glasgow, 1995</li>\r\n<li>B.E., Mehran UET Jamshoro, 1986</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>More than 38 years experience of teaching, Research and Academic Administration</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin-left: 1.0in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Alvi M.B., Mahoto, N.A., Al Reshan M.S., Unar M.A., Elmagzoub M.A., Shaikh A., Count Me Too: Sentiment Analysis of Roman Sindhi Script, Sage Open, Vol.13, No.3, 2023.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 1.0in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Memon A.A., Memon A.A., Uqaili M.A., Unar M.A., Effect of variable conduction angle on the losses of switched reluctance machine, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 42, No.2, April 2023.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 1.0in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Shaikh M., Siddiqui I.F., Arain Q., Unar M.A., Qureshi N.M.F., MDEV Model: A Novel Ensemble Based Transfer Learning Approach for Pneumonia Classification Using CXR Images, Computer Systems Science and Engineering, Vol. 46, No.1, 287-302, July-December 2023.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Ansari B., Unar M.A., Memon F., Shah S., Memon F.A., Modeling and Control of a Snake Robot Using SimMechanics, Sukkur IBA Journal of Emerging Technologies, Vol. 6, No.2, 2023.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Baloch Z., Shaikh F.K., Unar M.A.; CNN-LSTM-Based Late Sensor Fusion for Human Activity Recognition in Big Data Networks, Wireless Communications and Mobile Computing, August 2022.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Memon K.A., 