rials, Lahore, Pakistan, 2004.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Shaikh M.A.; Rajput A.Q.K.; Unar M.A., Virtual Reality Modeling Language Based Learning Environment for Teaching Mechanical Skills, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol 23, No. 2, pp. 103-108, 2004.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Junejo N.A.; Junejo N.A.; Unar M.A., MENeT: a monitoring and protocol analysis tool for LAN, 2004 IEEE/Sarnoff Symposium on Advances in Wired and Wireless Communications, NJ, USA, pp. 63-66, 2004.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Junejo N.A.; Junejo N.A.; Unar M.A.; Ethernet Traffic Analysis Using MNET, Proceedings of The First International Conference on Information and Communication Technologies: From Theory to Applications (ICTTA&rsquo;04), 19-23 April 2004, Damascus, Syria.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Junejo N.A.; Junejo N.A.; Unar M.A.; Low Bit-Rate Speech Coder for Multimedia Communications, Mehran University of Engineering and Technology, Vol 22, No. 4, pp. 243-252, 2003.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Unar M.A.; Rajput A.Q.K.., A Radial Basis Function Controller for a Large Tanker, Proceedings of the International Conference on Engineering Applications of Neural Networks, 08-10 September, Malaga, Spain, 2003.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Shaikh M.A.; Unar M.A.; Ansari A.S., Intelligent Aircraft Control System Using Neural Networks, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 22, No. 3, pp. 209-218,2003.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Ursani A.A.; Chowdhry B.S.; Unar M.A., Standard Keyboard for Information Interchange in Sindhi Language, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 22, No. 3, pp. 163-188, 2003.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Junejo N.A.; Unar M.A.; Junejo N.A., A New Approach to Internet Traffic Monitoring, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 22, No. 2, pp. 137-142, 2003.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Unar M.A.; Mahar R.B., Neural Network Applications for Hydraulic Characteristics of Drop and Jump, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 21, No. 3, pp. 133-140, 2002.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Unar M.A.; Maher R.B., Neural Network Applications in Civil Engineering, Proceedings of the Second International Civil Engineering Congress, 8th-11th November, Karachi, Pakistan, 2001.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Ursani A.A.; Chowdhry B.S.; Unar M.A., A Speech to Text System for Sindhi Language, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 20, No. 3, pp. 139-146, 2001.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Unar M.A.; Uquaili M.A.; Ansari A.S., Multilayer Perceptron Networks for Ship Steering Control, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 19, No.2, pp. 121-128, 2000.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Samejo A.A.; Rajput A.Q.K.; Unar M.A., Design, Development and Application of Browser for Surfing the Internet Smoothly and Efficiently in Specialized Environment, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 19, No. 2, pp. 109-120, 2000.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Unar M.A.; Samejo A.A.; Lakhani A., A Radial Basis Function Network Controller for a Supply Ship, Mehran University Research Journal of Engineering and Technology, Vol. 19, No. 1, pp. 59-66, 2000.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Unar M.A.; Chowdhry B.S.; Memon A.R., The Use of radial Basis Function Networks for the Intelligent Control of Ships, Proceedings of the International IEEE Conference on Millennium Technologies, Karachi, Pakistan, 1999.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 74.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">&middot;<span style="font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->Unar M.A.; Murray-Smith D.J., Automatic Steering of Ships Using