>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 'mu.unar@israuniversity.edu.pk', '+92 22 2030181 Ext. 250', 'EE-045', 'Electrical Engineering', '2026-06-10 05:36:30', '2026-06-10 05:36:30', NULL);
